{
  "stem": "13524.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Even if they thought I didn't receive all that-- I didn't perceive everything what was going on at home-- I absorbed everything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My parents spoke very often German because they were, during the war, under Austrian-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] under Austrian government.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So, especially if they didn't want us to understand, they spoke German, and that helped us to learn the language.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, constantly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was everyday occurrence-- here, there, everywhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we sort of-- like on a duck's back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't that important, unless it came close to the home-- it concerned me or concerned somebody close to me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, that did hurt very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that was nothing new.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Absolutely nothing new.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wouldn't say I belonged, but I did go to many, because that was Saturday afternoon.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had no television, and that was entertainment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would go to Bnei Akiva.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were gathering on the river Wisla.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was a picnic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were girls and boys.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I would say I already sort of noticed boys.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And if that afternoon finished, then we went to Shomer Hatzair with another girlfriend, because the boys were already more grown-up, and that was a more serious organization.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that I wasn't allowed to go to, because the boys were also older.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was tall, and I was accepted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the afternoon tea was good, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we always sort of travelled from one-- there was Dror.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember occasionally I would go there, to see what's going there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Actively I was too young, really, to belong.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had a lot of Judaism at home, so my parents did not particularly care that I do belong to any organization.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I did get the upbringing-- the Jewish upbringing-- at home.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
